# 🚀 A Ship That Fires Bullets

A 2D arcade game where the player controls a rocket ship to shoot down waves of alien invaders.

## 🔧 Features
- Player-controlled spaceship (arrow keys + spacebar)
- Alien fleet movement & speed increases per wave
- Bullet & collision detection
- Game over conditions
- Pygame-powered graphics and sound

## 🛠️ Tech Stack
- Python
- Pygame

